{"tid":694243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(點播率破10億) 「三郎」馬浚偉找數 貼完小雞雞祼照再晒赤膊相","createTime":"2018-06-08T07:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T09:40:53.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5647beb9ebd9ec3ab240c447997fd65967570976","tid":694243,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"「收視福將」、46歲嘅馬浚偉呢次孖視后胡定欣主演大台劇集《宮心計2深宮計》，佢哋對收視好有信心，胡定欣早前出席活動，佢大爆同馬仔劇中有「床戲」，佢哋拍時仲影咗床照私藏，胡定欣話如果收視創新高就公開呢批床照：「等到有30億收視啦，我隨時準備好公開呢批床照。」<br />\n<br />\n噚晚，馬仔就喺社交網貼咗自己一張BB祼照，佢趴喺長櫈，表情天然呆，但重要部位貼上小雞雞圖案，馬仔留言：「按目前的點播率，很快要破10億......那，三郎就發一張裸照，提早兌現承諾吧......#三郎祼照#宮心計2深宮計#」《蘋果》今日問番馬仔，佢短訊回覆：「因為之前訪問答應咗，過30億就放我和定欣拍戲的秘密床照，10億就我個人裸照，玩咋，大家開心。」馬仔又幾講口齒噃。<br />\n<br />\n今朝三郎終於找數，喺微博貼咗一張半身露膊照，仲送多個豬鼻㖭，留言：「好啦好啦，破10億了！兌現承諾，不過我又白又沒什麼肌肉，真的沒什麼看頭.....那就意思意思啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/152316_14d9595925ee9ef87b2a0830f246be80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F152316_14d9595925ee9ef87b2a0830f246be80.jpg&h=17aac39f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/152317_5fd967eade76d0c0ab835710eaba3ae0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F152317_5fd967eade76d0c0ab835710eaba3ae0.jpg&h=bce32e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/152317_8babd57dfaaf838482de96bfcdf6e8f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F152317_8babd57dfaaf838482de96bfcdf6e8f7.jpg&h=9f2004e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd626dc73d68a6a0b24ad8c6c75ae7910af4bf5f","tid":694243,"uid":77569,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85ce566db35955f71a65f7ed98e136fa667788de","tid":694243,"uid":146604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"係咪可以告佢傳播兒童色情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfdf1d44f79842c43488a8a0670ab8869739bf9","tid":694243,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"播左咁多集得10億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知唔知醜架"},{"pid":"d81751f3f6170b6e5eb3ba6095c2b1febbe36f74","tid":694243,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cfdf1d44f79842c43488a8a0670ab8869739bf9","tid":694243,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"播左咁多集得10億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知唔知醜架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"算係近排收視好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}